snippet.title: “Aquaman 2 Will FAIL Because of You” Jason Momoa Speaks To Amber Heard
snippet.description:
“Aquaman 2 Will FAIL Because of You” Jason Momoa Speaks To Amber Heard
Amber Heard has filed a lawsuit against her ex-husband Johnny Depp, alleging that he attacked her verbally and physically. Depp sued Heard for defamation after getting evidence of his innocence in the form of a leaked recording from 2015 and a statement from her hairstylist
